OL,3,CConsumer confidence in economy falls
OL,4,Cto lowest point this year
OL,6,FConsumer confidence in the UK economy
OL,7,Ffell during the last quarter to its
OL,8,Flowest point so far this year,
OL,9,Faccording to a survey.
OL,11,FKPMG's latest Consumer Pulse survey of
OL,12,F3,000 UK consumers saw the number of
OL,13,Fpeople feeling that the economy is
OL,14,Fworsening increase from 51% to 62% in
OL,15,Fthe last three months ` up from 43%
OL,16,Fsince 2025 began.
OL,18,FThe majority of consumers (58%)
OL,19,Fcontinue to feel financially secure,
OL,20,Fwith no change since the last quarter.
