OL,3,CConsumer confidence in economy falls
OL,4,Cto lowest point this year
OL,6,FLinda Ellett, head of consumer, retail
OL,7,Fand leisure at KPMG UK, said: "Rising
OL,8,Ffood inflation and news of higher
OL,9,Fenergy bills this autumn are two
OL,10,Flikely factors in the increase in
OL,11,Fconsumer pessimism about the UK
OL,12,Feconomy over the last quarter.
OL,14,F"Despite the majority of households
OL,15,Ffeeling secure in their current
OL,16,Fability to manage their household
OL,17,Fbudget, concern about what a worsening
OL,18,Feconomy will or could mean is leading
OL,19,Fconsumers to say they are cutting,
OL,20,Faltering or deferring spending.
