OL,6,F"As the Budget approaches, the
OL,7,FGovernment need to convince more
OL,8,Fhouseholds that the economy is heading
OL,9,Fin the right direction."
OL,11,FAs has been the case in previous
OL,12,FConsumer Pulse surveys this year,
OL,13,Feating out (40%) and takeaways (34%)
OL,14,Fwere the most common things people
OL,15,Freport spending less on this quarter
OL,16,Fcompared to last.
