OL,8,Fsupply challenges filter their way
OL,9,Fthrough to costs of food and drink `
OL,10,Fin both groceries and eating out `
OL,11,Fconsumers tell us that they are
OL,12,Fadapting their behaviour to manage
OL,13,Fthese higher costs.
